                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18110918-143-defend1060 t18110918-143-punish764"></join>
               Transported for Seven Years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex jury, before Mr. Recorder.</p>
